{"tid":658002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"膝頭對上就係脾","createTime":"2018-05-08T14:37:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T13:49:09.000Z","uid":135171,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5401839e5269405b0291d4f92636ed709567b77b","tid":658002,"uid":135171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟最近同朋友夾份租咗個細單位住<br />\n<br />\n日前新傢私送貨<br />\n咁我哋拆完貨就將啲紙皮放咗喺後樓梯收垃圾個位<br />\n大概有10幾個大紙皮箱咁上下<br />\n<br />\n今日個看更同我朋友講話個垃圾佬呻搬啲紙皮搬到好辛苦<br />\n佢叫我朋友俾返幾十蚊個垃圾佬喎<br />\n話交比佢 佢聽日幫我哋交比個垃圾佬<br />\n<br />\n我朋友就答個看更聽日俾 打算俾$20佢<br />\n我就話又唔係搬傢私 又有𨋢答 紙皮又可以賣錢 唔使俾$20佢<br />\n唔知大家點睇呢？<br />\n<br />\n👍🏼= 俾你老母，膝頭對上就係脾<br />\n👎🏼= 算啦，都係廿蚊啫"},{"pid":"21d27169fe28daee0eb3d0e2295806a174a86874","tid":658002,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"似個看更想昆你幾廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7590a91c9525049b48d1705881d927b4f0d4d62","tid":658002,"uid":78336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21d27169fe28daee0eb3d0e2295806a174a86874","tid":658002,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:42:18.000Z","msg":"似個看更想昆你幾廿蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:55:18.000Z","msg":"咪就係<br />\nd低賤垃圾看更野就唔做<br />\n日日淨係識訓<br />\n等到新年就呃利是<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bf993a23a5c3989cbadc48bb08012487777c01","tid":658002,"uid":45368,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"其實係&quot;髀&quot;<br />\n&quot;脾&quot;係內臟"},{"pid":"0cc2c9befdba660f0d8b7946d8e2456a8311a9a5","tid":658002,"uid":160122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"咁樣要畀$20蚊真係&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77d2989aa738bdf248f0f5d6b885ebefacf8924","tid":658002,"uid":144466,"like":0,"d